## 4. Gamification (Engagement)

### Focus RPG System

- 1 minute of focus = 1 XP
- Leveling up unlocks:
  - Exclusive ambient sounds (e.g., "Space Station", "Medieval Library")
  - Special YouTube background presets
  - Custom themes and visual effects

### Loot Drops & Rewards

- Completing 2-hour session drops a "Coffee Break" item (15-minute timer that doesn't break streak)
- Rare drops for milestone achievements
- Collectible badges for different study patterns

### Achievements System

- "Night Owl" - Study past midnight
- "Early Bird" - Study before 6 AM
- "Marathon Runner" - 4+ hour session
- "Consistency King" - 30-day streak

