## 5. AI Study Buddy Tools - Premium Feature

### Flashcard Generator

- Paste paragraph of notes
- AI generates 5 key flashcards automatically
- Export to Anki or Quizlet format

### Socratic Mode

- AI never gives direct answers
- Asks guiding questions to help users solve problems themselves
- Encourages critical thinking

### Summary Writer

- At end of session, user speaks voice note summarizing what they learned
- AI cleans it up into bulleted list for session log
- Creates searchable study notes automatically

### Study Technique Suggestions

- Based on subject and session patterns
- Recommends techniques: Pomodoro, Feynman Method, Spaced Repetition
- Personalized learning style analysis

